name: Patrick Dominguez
what_you_do: Transform your life and business. Discover what's blocking you from having the financial abundance, the love relationship, or the inner peace you really want. Become a powerful creator of what you're truly longing for – in business, relationship, health and inner peace.
who_you_serve: Ambitious and visionary coaches and business owners
social_proof: Co-founded a multi-million dollar business coaching company with 25 employees, and in 14+ years has coached and trained over 10,000 business owners worldwide.
business_focus: Coaching ambitious and visionary coaches and business owners to create a greater level of impact in the world while breaking into 6-figure and 7-figure revenue levels.
